1. *Uzmemo* kartu za autobus i krenemo prema Novom Sadu. (We will take a bus ticket and go to Novi Sad.)

2. *Uzmeš* li još jednu kafu? (Will you take one more coffee?)

3. Ona *uzme* svoj deo plaće i ode. (She will take her share of the pay and leave.)

4. Ovi učenici *uzmu* svoje školske torbe i krenu na čas. (These students will take their school bags and go to class.)

5. On *uzme* teglu s kolačima i ode do svoje sobe. (He will take the jar of cakes and go to his room.)